# wxSudoku Install Guide

#---- Source Install Any OS ----#

wxSudoku doesn't need to be installed to be used. It can be run by running
either Sudoku.py or Sudoku.pyw. If you wish to install it simply install it
like any other python module.

python setup.py install


#---- OSX Install ----#

1) Double click on the disk image (dmg)
2) Copy the app to your Applications Folder
3) Eject the disk image


#---- Windows Install ----#

1) Double click on the installer
2) Follow the on screen instructions
